# 🛡️ Cyber Hygiene Checklist Web App

This is a simple and user-friendly web application designed to help users practice good **cyber hygiene** every day. Built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**, it includes a login page, daily tips, and weekly reminders.

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 Login Page
- 📋 Daily Checklist Dashboard
- 📅 Weekly Cyber Hygiene Reminders
- 🌗 Dark Mode
- 💪 Password Strength Checker
- 🧠 Tip of the Day (rotates daily)

## 🎯 Goal

To promote consistent and easy-to-follow cybersecurity habits, especially for beginners and students.

## 🛠️ Built With

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- GitHub Pages (for hosting)

